  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/253/mode/1up">253</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/253/mode/1up">253</ref>.</p>
<p>ic cūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, uriccoṟka ṭiṟattuppaṭuvatōr ilakkaṇam uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai : iṭaiccol lellām vēṟṟumaic collātaṟku evvāṟuriyavāyiṉamaṉ, avvurimai uriccoṟkaṇṇum eytum eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>ummai iṟantatu taḻīiyiṟṟu. uriccol lellām vēṟṟumaiccol eṉṟatu mēṟkūṟiya iṭaiccollēpōla uriccollum tāmāka nillā, peyarum viṉaiyum aṭaintu poruḷvēṟupaṭutaluṭaiya, atu nōkki yeṉpatu. irutalaiyāka avaṟṟai vēṟṟumaiccol eṉṟavāṟu.	(59)</p>
 </body>
  </text>

